Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.16,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:36.97,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:04.87,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.01,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:22.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:27.10,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:34.03,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Education?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kyouiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: "polite"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:01:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Teinei-na.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Individual"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tandoku-no, koko-no,dokutoku-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Trend?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sonohou e muke, katamuku, hucho...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Unbecoming?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Niawa nai, husouou-na...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be back in school beginning today, Shinobu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mid-terms are next week, and she feels much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we have lunch together some time. The three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinonu Mariko-san is coming back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was partly my fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't say everything is going to be the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I'd rather that we forget all the unpleasant things,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...and concentrate on these coming mid-terms instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the car! Right here is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you wanted, a Jean Saint-Teauille first edition...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so precious, you said you'd never part with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd prefer I weren't so... changeable?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}11. Under the Elm Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorority members: please assemble at the Sorority House at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Sorority members!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to the Sorority House!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll study there for the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The senior members always help the junior members study.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, mid-terms start next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority expects all our new members to do well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the first major exam for our new members...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I must remind you that our rules require that you place in the top 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The top 50!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Our senior members are here to help our junior members study.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our Sorority's tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you'd like to see the kind of questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...you can expect to find in Seiran's exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it is the first day, we'll meet at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can enjoy tea and study.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful to be able to go to Miya-sama's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you all this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You were hospitalized recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that being healthy is another requirement of the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm glad your hospitalization was a short one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It may start raining...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so beautiful this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Jean Saint-Teauille to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorority members are getting together at my house today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take you to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me at five o'clock under the elm tree in the court yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After school, all junior members were divided into groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We got into the senior members's cars...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...and headed to Fukiko-sama's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The darkened sky seemed ready to shed raindrops like tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I was excited, I also felt somewhat anxious and uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I was feeling a premonition of the unforgettable event...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...which was about to unfold before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be serving tea and cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this {\i1}"Nubatama-no"{\i0} is a {\i1}Makura Kotoba{\i0} modifying "night".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Makura Kotoba{\i0} will be covered on the mid-term.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this requires factoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Underline in red the rule on page 90 of your text book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an important point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spring goes, and summer comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ame-no-kaguyama, where the gods dry their white robes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not only memorize this poem,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but make sure you understand the meaning also.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wherefore du I hesitate, though my heart is at your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Next, the Spring Poem by Ootomo Yakamochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though the sky is clouded with snowflakes falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The nightingale chirps in the garden of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If one could die from only a though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surely I would have dies one thousan times by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's raining hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue, Misonoo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dark of the night is a painful thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will the moon I await not shine for me soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Misonoo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I'm sorry... I left my French reading book and notebook at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go back to pick them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppose we study mathematics instead of French today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I have a homework due tomorrow, and I need my notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Then I'll have my driver take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't hear of it! It's okay, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn! I've forgotten my umbrella...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! I'm very grateful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain during this season is very cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that? Miya-sama lavishes her attention on Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the studying Miya-sama has been teaching only Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"It"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What "It"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumour that it was Miya-sama alone who insisted that Misonoo-san be chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, what do you mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take another break for tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That song... it's the one Saint-Juste is always playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Exhaustion and relief, combined with the steady soothing sound of raindrops,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:14:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...made the classroom feel like a quiet haven at the bottom of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it was dark outside. I had been asleep over an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I've got to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama! Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're soaking! You'll catch a cold, Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was she there, wet and alone under that elm tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...I had no idea then and what could she be thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She was cold as ice, soaked to the bone, and couldn't even talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I took her to her home, using the address on her student ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it! Come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Itlu-chome, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! 1-17-15 Maison d'Eduard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking you to your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was to wait there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...wait... for Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddaya think you're doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need this kind of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To the elm tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the opposite direction from your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She's... feverish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I must get back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you mustn't! You have a fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to go home! Please go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise... otherwise I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sweet peas...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... I'll give these to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,don't pay any mind to me... anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make Kukiko-sama wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to take me to her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me to wait, at 5 o'clock, under the elm tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Miya-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama is already at her home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a bad girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was no lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I must hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama... Fukiko-sama, I'm coming right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... Saint-Juste-sama... you mustn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No... wait... I'll open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirrors?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirrors...and so many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Everyone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no "everyone" here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She lives here alone, surrounded by mirrors?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie La Poupee...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the bathroom? Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.71,0:23:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to dry off and change right now! Which way is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie La Poupee....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie La Poupee...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:13.84,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:19.35,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:24.94,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.94,0:24:30.40,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:36.70,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.70,0:24:42.16,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.16,0:24:44.87,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.87,0:24:47.71,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.71,0:24:50.09,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.09,0:24:55.39,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.35,0:25:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi arrives at Rei's apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.62,0:25:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She slaps Rei and angrily rips the bracelet from her wrist!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.82,0:25:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And Nanako can now see what was concealed beneath the bracelet...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.37,0:25:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: The Scar
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.21,0:25:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
